<body>

  

    <!-- Dashboard page wrapper start -->
    <div class="page">
        <header>
            @await Html.PartialAsync("_HeaderDashboard")
        </header>

        <!-- Start app-content-area -->
        <div class="app-content-area p-relative">
            <div class="app-content-wrap">
                <div class="generator-box-wrapper generator-gap">
                    <div class="single-item-generator">
                        <div class="chat-box">
                            <div class="chat-box-author d-flex flex-wrap justify-end align-start gap-20">
                                <div class="author-text-box d-flex align-center gap-15">
                                    <div class="d-flex align-center gap-10">
                                        <button type="button" class="author-text-btn bd-tooltip-show">
                                            <i class="ri-file-copy-line"></i>
                                            <span class="bd-tooltip">Copy</span>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="author-text-btn bd-tooltip-show">
                                            <i class="ri-edit-fill"></i>
                                            <span class="bd-tooltip">Edit message</span>
                                        </button>
                                        <button type="button" class="author-text-btn bd-tooltip-show">
                                            <i class="ri-delete-bin-line"></i>
                                            <span class="bd-tooltip">Delete</span>
                                        </button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text">Give me an article idea for a blog post</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="author">
                                    <div class="author-thumb">
                                        <img src="../images/avatar/main-user.webp" alt="user">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="chat-box">
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-start align-start gap-20">
                                <div class="ekoai-thumb"><img src="../images/logo/favicon.svg" alt=""></div>
                                <div class="ekoai-body">
                                    <p class="description">Here’s an intriguing article idea that explores the
                                        intersection of productivity and mental well-being. It presents a perspective
                                        that goes against the traditional idea of constantly being "busy" and working
                                        harder.</p>

                                    <h4 class="text-hading-title">"The Productivity Paradox: Why Doing Less Can Help You
                                        Achieve More"</h4>

                                    <p class="description">In this blog post, we’ll challenge the traditional notion of
                                        productivity, exploring the counterintuitive idea that working less can actually
                                        help you accomplish more. With the rise of "hustle culture" in modern society,
                                        many people believe that working non-stop and maintaining a busy schedule are
                                        the keys to success. However, this constant drive for more can lead to burnout,
                                        lack of focus, and diminishing returns. This article offers a fresh perspective
                                        on how taking time for rest and reflection can lead to greater long-term
                                        success.</p>

                                    <p class="description">The post will delve into:</p>

                                    <ul class="generator-info-list sl-number-counts">
                                        <li><strong>The 80/20 Rule (Pareto Principle):</strong> How focusing on the
                                            few
                                            things that truly matter can yield more results than trying to do
                                            everything
                                            at once.</li>
                                        <li><strong>Time-Blocking Techniques:</strong> How to effectively manage
                                            your
                                            schedule by prioritizing tasks, scheduling focused time for deep work,
                                            and
                                            avoiding distractions.</li>
                                        <li><strong>The Importance of Saying "No":</strong> Why learning to decline
                                            non-essential tasks and requests can free up valuable time and energy
                                            for
                                            more meaningful work.</li>
                                        <li><strong>Mindful Rest and Recovery:</strong> How taking regular breaks
                                            and
                                            embracing the power of rest can improve both mental and physical
                                            well-being,
                                            leading to enhanced productivity when you return to work.</li>
                                    </ul>

                                    <p class="description">Additionally, the article will offer actionable tips on how
                                        to:</p>

                                    <ul class="generator-info-list sl-number-counts">
                                        <li> Streamline your daily routines to focus on high-impact tasks.</li>
                                        <li> Use time management tools like Pomodoro and time-blocking to optimize work
                                            hours.</li>
                                        <li> Incorporate habits that promote mental clarity, such as meditation, deep
                                            breathing, and walking outdoors.</li>
                                        <li> Understand the importance of downtime and how it can prevent burnout and
                                            lead to sustained productivity.</li>
                                    </ul>

                                    <p class="description">By following these strategies, readers can learn how to adopt
                                        a more balanced approach to work that emphasizes quality over quantity, allowing
                                        them to accomplish more while preserving their well-being.</p>

                                    <p class="description">Would you like a more specific angle or a different topic
                                        altogether? Let me know if you have a particular niche in mind, and I’d be happy
                                        to tailor the content further!</p>

                                    <div class="generator-info">
                                        <p class="description">Would you like to explore another idea, or perhaps
                                            customize this one further?</p>
                                        <div class="generator-info-btn d-flex align-center gap-05">
                                            <button class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show" type="button">
                                                <i class="ri-volume-up-line"></i>
                                                <span class="bd-tooltip bottom">Read aloud</span>
                                            </button>
                                            <button class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show" type="button">
                                                <i class="ri-thumb-up-line"></i>
                                                <span class="bd-tooltip bottom">Good response</span>
                                            </button>
                                            <button class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show" type="button">
                                                <i class="ri-thumb-down-line"></i>
                                                <span class="bd-tooltip bottom">Bad response</span>
                                            </button>
                                            <button class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show" type="button">
                                                <i class="ri-edit-box-line"></i>
                                                <span class="bd-tooltip bottom">Edit in canvas</span>
                                            </button>
                                            <button class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show" type="button">
                                                <i class="ri-share-line"></i>
                                                <span class="bd-tooltip bottom">Share</span>
                                            </button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- new chat form -->
            <div class="new-chat-form-wrapper">
                <div class="new-chat-form">
                    <form action="#">
                        <textarea placeholder="Write Message.."></textarea>
                        <div class="new-chat-input d-flex align-center justify-between gap-30 mt-15">
                            <div class="">
                                <div class="generator-info-btn d-flex align-center gap-05">
                                    <div class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show">
                                        <i class="ri-attachment-line"></i>
                                        <input type="file" class="input-file" name="myfile" multiple="">
                                        <span class="bd-tooltip">Attach files</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <button class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show" type="button">
                                        <i class="ri-image-line"></i>
                                        <span class="bd-tooltip">Search Image</span>
                                    </button>
                                    <button class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show" type="button">
                                        <i class="ri-file-video-line"></i>
                                        <span class="bd-tooltip">Search Video</span>
                                    </button>
                                    <button class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show" type="button">
                                        <i class="ri-global-line"></i>
                                        <span class="bd-tooltip">Search Web</span>
                                    </button>
                                    <button class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show" type="button">
                                        <i class="ri-file-text-line"></i>
                                        <span class="bd-tooltip">Search Text</span>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="">
                                <button class="generator-btn bd-tooltip-show" type="button">
                                    <i class="ri-upload-line"></i>
                                    <span class="bd-tooltip">Message is empty</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- new chat form -->
        </div>
        <!-- end app-content-area -->
    </div>
    <!-- Dashboard page wrapper end -->

    <!-- back to top area start -->
    <div class="progress-wrap mobile-right">
        <svg class="progress-circle svg-content" width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="-1 -1 102 102">
            <path d="M50,1 a49,49 0 0,1 0,98 a49,49 0 0,1 0,-98" />
        </svg>
    </div>
    <!-- back to top area end -->

    <!-- switcher area start -->
    <div class="theme-switcher">
        <i class="ri-sun-line change-theme" id="theme-button"></i>
    </div>
